      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mb-6">Uses, Specifications &amp; Capacities — Offshore oil and gas platforms rely on disc stack centrifuges for diesel fuel purification, engine lube oil maintenance, and bilge water treatment in explosion-proof configurations.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
