        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-heading text-navy mb-4">Capacity</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">As previously mentioned, disc-stack centrifuges have different processing capacities for different fluids based on the fluid's viscosity. The following table lists the different capacities of select disc-stack centrifuge models for different fluids.</p>

